lead_paragraph: U.S. defense officials say the United States targeted a senior Islamic State commander in an airstrike last week in Syria and are assessing whether he may have been killed.

headline.main: Officials: US Airstrike Targeted IS Military Commander
headline.print_headline: Officials: US Airstrike Targeted IS Military Commander
